msgctxt "QL_HatenoMini_LoveInsects_Answer"
msgid ""
"Prima said her dream is to have a collection of\n"
"100 <1.se_co>restless crickets<2.re_co>.\n"
"\n"
"You should break the news to <3.se_co>Manny<4.re_co>."
msgstr ""

#. 1: set_colour (red)
#. 2: reset_colour
msgctxt "QL_HatenoMini_LoveInsects_Desc"
msgid ""
"A friend of Manny's wants more than anything\n"
"to catch the eye of Prima, owner of the\n"
"Ton Pu Inn.\n"
"\n"
"All you have to do is <1.se_co>ask<2.re_co> Prima what she\n"
"loves most."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_HatenoMini_LoveInsects_Finish"
msgid ""
"You delivered the 10 restless crickets to\n"
"Manny and received a reward.\n"
"\n"
"He confessed that he was the one who wanted\n"
"to catch Prima's eye. His plan now is to find the\n"
"other 90 restless crickets on his own and\n"
"present them to Prima when he asks her out\n"
"on a date.\n"
"\n"
"It seems you're off the hook..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_HatenoMini_LoveInsects_Name"
msgid "A Gift for My Beloved"
msgstr ""

